ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 157 - (Yukon) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 157 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to YUKON with respect to the RAINSTORM which affected the area south of Beaver Creek from June 6 to 8, 2012, inclusive.
